130
0:05:55.608,000 --> 0:05:56,000
Parlez aux personnes transgenres.

131
0:05:57.653,000 --> 0:05:58,000
Écoutez-nous.

132
0:05:59.587,000 --> 0:06:,000
Soyez nos porte-voix.

133
